  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>When to ski, or not to ski, that is (of course) the question. Whether you’re after high-speed thrills, gentle meandering or if you’ve got snow on the brain, there’s a month for that.</p>
<p>To help you decide when to hit the slopes next season, take a look at our guide on where to go skiing and snowboarding, based on the most snow sure ski resorts in Europe by month.</p>
<h3>Best Places to Ski in December</h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you can't wait to be back in the mountains, you'll want to start skiing in early December. Take a look at the best places to ski in December, offering you an enchanting experience of snow and sparkle during the magical festive season.</span></p>
